  "tutorial_screen": {
    "mascot": [80, 315],
    "textbox": [120, 340],
    "arrow_offset": [-100, 0],
    "ok_button_offset": [-200, 0],
    "steps": [
      {
        "step_idx": 0,
        "text": "Welcome!\nIn this game, you will be managing an amusement park.",
        "highlight_pos": [990, 335],
        "include_arrow": false,
        "include_ok_button": true
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 1,
        "text": "The main goal of the game is to maximize your park's value.",
        "highlight_pos": [1620, 134],
        "include_arrow": true,
        "include_ok_button": true
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 2,
        "text": "Let's start by placing a ride.\nNotice that your action tab is currently on 'rides'",
        "highlight_pos": [1020, 565],
        "include_arrow": true,
        "include_ok_button": true
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 3,
        "text": "Within this tab, you can choose the type of ride to place.\nFor now, let's select the carousel by clicking on it.",
        "highlight_pos": [1075, 690],
        "include_arrow": true,
        "include_ok_button": false
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 4,
        "text": "You can see the cost of the action under the action button.",
        "highlight_pos": [1420, 942],
        "include_arrow": true,
        "include_ok_button": true
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 5,
        "text": "There are multiple colors available for each ride.\nLet's see how expensive a green carousel is.",
        "highlight_pos": [1142, 918],
        "include_arrow": true,
        "include_ok_button": false
      },
      
      {
        "step_idx": 6,
        "text": "You can check how much money you currently have by looking at\nyour info panel.",
        "highlight_pos": [1620, 176],
        "include_arrow": true,
        "include_ok_button": true
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 7,
        "text": "Since there isn't currently enough money for the green\ncarousel, let's go back to the yellow one.",
        "highlight_pos": [1050, 918],
        "include_arrow": true,
        "include_ok_button": false
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 8,
        "text": "For rides, you need to input a ticket price. Click on the box\nand type a number. Note the max price underneath.",
        "highlight_pos": [1400, 842],
        "include_arrow": true,
        "include_ok_button": false
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 9,
        "text": "Great! Now, click on the place button.",
        "highlight_pos": [1430, 907],
        "include_arrow": true,
        "include_ok_button": false
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 10,
        "text": "You can see the button now says 'Placing...'.\nNow place by clicking on a tile in the grid.",
        "highlight_pos": [550, 650],
        "include_arrow": true,
        "include_ok_button": false
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 11,
        "text": "After performing an action, the day starts and guests visit\nyour park. You can always check the day's progression.",
        "highlight_pos": [1003, 0],
        "include_arrow": true,
        "include_ok_button": true
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 12,
        "text": "You can also control the speed of the day using the playback\npanel, ...",
        "highlight_pos": [1620, 13],
        "include_arrow": true,
        "include_ok_button": true
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 13,
        "text": "..., or skip animating the day entirely by unchecking the\nanimate day box.",
        "highlight_pos": [1760, 13],
        "include_arrow": true,
        "include_ok_button": false
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 14,
        "text": "Well done! You've completed a full day. Check the info panel\nto see how the day went. Note: profit includes action cost.",
        "highlight_pos": [1620, 220],
        "include_arrow": true,
        "include_ok_button": true 
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 15,
        "text": "This is your park rating. It increases with\nguest happiness, high excitement, and balanced intensity...",
        "highlight_pos": [1615, 345],
        "include_arrow": true,
        "include_ok_button": true
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 16,
        "text": "...and decreases with low cleanliness, or when rides or\nshops go out of service too frequently.",
        "highlight_pos": [1615, 345],
        "include_arrow": true,
        "include_ok_button": true
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 17,
        "text": "This is the capacity of your park,\nwhich is determined by the cumulative capacity of your rides",
        "highlight_pos": [1754, 345],
        "include_arrow": true,
        "include_ok_button": true
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 18,
        "text": "This is the number of guests that visited your park today",
        "highlight_pos": [1615, 400],
        "include_arrow": true,
        "include_ok_button": true
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 19,
        "text": "And lastly, this is the average amount of money spent\nby each guest.",
        "highlight_pos": [1755, 400],
        "include_arrow": true,
        "include_ok_button": true
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 20,
        "text": "You can find even more information about your park\nin the aggregate stats panel.",
        "highlight_pos": [1620, 680],
        "include_arrow": true,
        "include_ok_button": true
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 21,
        "text": "Now let's place a shop. Select the shop tab by clicking on it.",
        "highlight_pos": [1105, 565],
        "include_arrow": true,
        "include_ok_button": false
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 22,
        "text": "Shop types include drink, food, and specialty.\nPick any you want.",
        "highlight_pos": [1075, 690],
        "include_arrow": true,
        "include_ok_button": false
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 23,
        "text": "Shops require an item price and an order quantity. First input\nthe item price, which is how much guests will pay for an item.",
        "highlight_pos": [1220, 790],
        "include_arrow": true,
        "include_ok_button": false
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 24,
        "text": "Next, input the order quantity. This determines how many items\nto stock each day.",
        "highlight_pos": [1400, 790],
        "include_arrow": true,
        "include_ok_button": false
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 25,
        "text": "Now, place the shop. Note: both rides and shops can only\nbe placed on an empty tile beside a path.",
        "highlight_pos": [1430, 907],
        "include_arrow": true,
        "include_ok_button": false
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 26,
        "text": "Excellent! Now navigate to the staff tab.",
        "highlight_pos": [1190, 565],
        "include_arrow": true,
        "include_ok_button": false
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 27,
        "text": "Place any staff you want.\nNote: staff can only be placed on a path or in an attraction.",
        "highlight_pos": [1430, 907],
        "include_arrow": true,
        "include_ok_button": false
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 28,
        "text": "There's also a research tab. In medium difficulty, research is\nrequired to unlock higher colored entities.",
        "highlight_pos": [1275, 565],
        "include_arrow": true,
        "include_ok_button": false
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 29,
        "text": "The guest survey tab allows you to survey guests.\nNote: results become visible once a survey has been completed.",
        "highlight_pos": [1360, 565],
        "include_arrow": true,
        "include_ok_button": false
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 30,
        "text": "Finally, there's the wait and sandbox tab.",
        "highlight_pos": [1530, 565],
        "include_arrow": true,
        "include_ok_button": false
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 31,
        "text": "In sandbox mode, you can find a range of additonal actions\nhere to help you experiment.",
        "highlight_pos": [1050, 825],
        "include_arrow": true,
        "include_ok_button": true
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 32,
        "text": "In evaluation, this tab only contains wait, which allows you\nto start the day without performing any actions.",
        "highlight_pos": [1200, 665],
        "include_arrow": true,
        "include_ok_button": true
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 33,
        "text": "Finally, checkout the game's documentation in the top right.\nIt includes detailed game mechanics and useful tips.",
        "highlight_pos": [1950, 0],
        "include_arrow": false,
        "include_ok_button": true
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 34,
        "text": "And that's it! You now know all the basics needed\nto play.",
        "highlight_pos": [990, 335],
        "include_arrow": false,
        "include_ok_button": true
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 35,
        "text": "Feel free to hang out here. When you are ready, click the\nend button in the sandbox tab to return to the main menu.",
        "highlight_pos": [0, 0],
        "include_arrow": false,
        "include_ok_button": false
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 36,
        "text": "Uh oh! You played an invalid action.\nNote: The day will still run as if you made no action.",
        "highlight_pos": [990, 335],
        "include_arrow": false,
        "include_ok_button": true
      },
      {
        "step_idx": 37,
        "text": "Check the error box up top to see what went wrong.\n When the day is done, try again to see if you can fix it.",
        "highlight_pos": [100, 10],
        "include_arrow": false,
        "include_ok_button": false
      }
    ]
  },
